name: #0 GRAVITY Rainbow at the end of times
description: We are at the beginning of change. At the end of times. As we move through the metaverse, we discover digital creations of unimaginable impact. Unexplored but at the same time symbols in a new medium. A dedication to the main actors in our universe. The sculpture HODL MY HAND drifts past our gaze and at the same time reflects the standard in simple image manipulation. FOMO and HODL take the wheel like 2 hands. Through a mass of creations #0 GRAVITY series tracks the unique orbit around galaxy Mamadou Sow 22 1
